<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bạʿln ḍʿfy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̉wqạt ktyr mn gẖyr tfsyr bạjry wrạʾ kẖṭty
 wywm bʿd ywm sẖrwry tzyd wtḍyʿ kmạn ạ̉bdyty
 ạ̉nạ jạy wbạʿln ḍʿfy qdạm jlạlk wạ̉nḥny
 fk qywdy nwr gẖywmy wmn ṭryqy rdny
 qwyny byk wạsndny rby fy mḥnty
 ṣlḥ ʿywby wạgẖfr ly ạ̹nt kẖṭty
 ạ̉wqạt ktyr ygẖyb ạlḍmyr
 wạ̉nsạk bạ̉mr sẖhwty
 wạfḍl ʿl y̱ḥạly mạfysẖ tgẖyyr
 wạ̉kẖsr krạmty bzlty</lyrics>
<author>rymwn ʿyd, mynạ ṣbḥy</author>
<hymn_number>9961</hymn_number>
</song>